data.description: A must see beautiful and unique Property that is on an over sized corner lot. Landscaping is well maintained and property has a five car garage. There is storage building in the back yard, high ceilings, New lighting in kitchen ad dining area, Life Source Water system, a chef kitchen and to many upgrades to list. Solar panels are owned. Owners will need a two to three week leaseback after closing to remove all personal belongings.
